<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
<title>Página Não Encontrada - Furina do Discord</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@500;700&family=Raleway:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css" />
<style>
  /* Reset */
  * {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  body {
    font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at top, #0b1c3a 0%, #08172e 70%, #06152a 100%);
    color: white;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  /* Container para sidebar e main */
  .container {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    min-height: calc(100vh - 70px); /* altura total menos header e footer */
  }

  /* Sidebar */
  .sidebar {
    position: fixed;
    top: 60px; /* abaixo do header */
    left: 0;
    width: 220px;
    height: calc(100vh - 130px); /* full height menos header + footer */
    background: rgba(6, 21, 42, 0.9);
    padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    z-index: 1001;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .sidebar.hidden {
    transform: translateX(-100%);
  }

  .sidebar a {
    color: #3DD1D9;
    text-decoration: none;
    background: none;
    padding: 0;
    border-radius: 0;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .sidebar a:hover {
    color: #1ec9cc;
  }

  /* Header */
  header {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 60px;
    background: rgba(6, 21, 42, 0.9);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    z-index: 1002;
    justify-content: space-between;
    color: #3DD1D9;
  }

  header .logo {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  header .logo img {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid #3DD1D9;
    margin-right: 10px;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  /* Botão menu mobile */
  .menu-toggle {
    display: none;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: #3DD1D9;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  /* Main */
  main {
    margin-left: 220px;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin-top: 60px;
  }

  main img {
    max-width: 300px;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 0 15px #3DD1D9;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  main h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #3DD1D9;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  main p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #DDEEFF;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  main a {
    background: #3DD1D9;
    color: #06152a;
    padding: 0.8rem 1.8rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.3s;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  main a:hover {
    background: #2bb8bf;
  }

  /* Footer */
  footer {
    background-color: #0a1e33;
    padding: 1.5rem 1rem 1.5rem 240px;
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 2px solid #3DD1D9;
    color: #A0CFE8;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    width: 100%;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    position: relative;
    left: 0;
    bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Mobile Responsivo */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .sidebar {
      position: fixed;
      top: 60px;
      left: 0;
      height: calc(100vh - 120px);
      width: 220px;
      background: rgba(6, 21, 42, 0.95);
      padding-top: 2rem;
      transform: translateX(-100%);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
      z-index: 1002;
    }

    .sidebar.show {
      transform: translateX(0);
    }

    header {
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }

    main {
      margin: 60px 1rem 2rem 1rem;
      max-width: 100%;
      margin-left: 0;
    }

    footer {
      padding-left: 1rem;
      margin-left: 0;
    }

    .menu-toggle {
      display: block;
    }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="/img/furinaTriste.png" alt="Furina" />
      Furina do Discord
    </div>
    <button class="menu-toggle" aria-label="Abrir menu" onclick="toggleSidebar()">
      <i class="fas fa-bars"></i>
    </button>
  </header>

  <div class="container">
    <nav class="sidebar" id="sidebar">
      <a href="/">Início</a>
      <a href="/termos">Termos de Serviço</a>
      <a href="/privacidade">Política de Privacidade</a>
      <a href="/comandos">Lista de Comandos</a>
      <a href="https://discord.gg/MkneaxC8jY" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Servidor Oficial</a>
    </nav>

    <main>
      <img src="/img/furinaTriste.png" alt="Furina triste" />
      <h1>Ah não... Essa página desapareceu como lágrimas na chuva!</h1>
      <p>
        Você tentou acessar um caminho que não existe neste reino. Mas não desanime! Volte para a página inicial e continue sua aventura ao meu lado.
      </p>
      <a href="/">Voltar ao Início</a>
    </main>
  </div>

  <footer>
    &copy; 2025 Furina do Discord - Todos os direitos reservados.
  </footer>

<script>
  function toggleSidebar() {
    const sidebar = document.getElementById('sidebar');
    sidebar.classList.toggle('show');
  }

  // Fecha sidebar clicando fora no mobile
  window.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
    const sidebar = document.getElementById('sidebar');
    const toggleBtn = document.querySelector('.menu-toggle');
    if (!sidebar.contains(e.target) && !toggleBtn.contains(e.target)) {
      sidebar.classList.remove('show');
    }
  });
</script>
</body>
</html>
